..TEXT:
|n$e fu per fantasia gi@a mai compreso~: |Fantasia~,
here as elsewhere in the ^Comedy~, refers specifically to that
human faculty of the mind which receives images; hence |compreso~
means "grasped," "taken in."  Cf. ^Purg.~ XVII, 25, and see the
corresponding note.
