..TEXT:
|'l vostro~: That is, ^cielo~ {v. 28}, this heaven of
Jupiter.  |non l'apprende con velame~: Whereas souls in other
spheres look up to the Thrones for the reflection of God's
judgment and justice, it appears that the souls in the heaven of
Jupiter (this heaven of justice) see God's justice directly.
