..TEXT:
|Sapete come attento~... |vecchio~: The souls
that make up the eagle know Dante's past and present thoughts in
regard to the question that has troubled him for so long, and
they will soon proceed to read those thoughts and formulate his
"doubt" (vss. 70-78).
