|che, ben che~... |profondo~: The image
effectively conveys, with |pelago~, what is often referred to as
the abyss of God's counsel (^Par.~ VII, 94-95).  |proda~:
"Shore."  |pelago~: The deep (cf. ^Inf.~ I, 23).  |@eli~ = ^vi @e~
(unaccented ^li~ = ^vi~).  |lui~: |Il fondo~, vs. 61. "It [the
bottom] is there, but its depth conceals it."
